text: Kiandra "KiKi" Layne (born December 10, 1991) is an American actress.KiKi Layne, ‘Beale Street’s’ Breakout Star, Has a 4 a.m. Moment, New York Times, Sept. 11, 2018 She is best known for her starring roles in If Beale Street Could Talk (2018), the drama Native Son (2019), the action superhero movie The Old Guard (2020), and the romantic comedy Coming 2 America (2021). ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:DePaul University alumni Category:American movie actors Category:American voice actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:Actors from Cincinnati
